	<div class="content-container site-container">
		<div id="main" class="site-main">
						<div class="content-wrap">
				<article id="post-30489" class="entry content-bg single-entry post-30489 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-cheesecake category-chocolate category-dessert category-fathers-day category-summer tag-cheesecake tag-chocolate tag-cream-cheese tag-heavy-cream tag-no-bake-cheesecake tag-peanut-butter grow-content-body">
	<div class="entry-content-wrap">
		
<div class="entry-content single-content">
	<!-- [element-90662] --><p></p>
<!-- [/element-90662] --><!-- [element-2926] -->
<p class="kt-adv-heading2926_183d80-7f wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading2926_183d80-7f"><em>This post may contain affiliate links. Read our&nbsp;<a href="/policies/privacy-policy/">disclosure policy</a>.</em></p>
<!-- [/element-2926] --><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="180" height="180" src="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-1-180x180.jpg" data-pin-media="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-1.jpg" data-pin-title="To Hot To Bake? Make This No Bake Cheescake!" data-pin-description="When it’s way too hot to turn on the oven, this is what I make! A super creamy no bake cheesecake with a graham cracker crust, fluffy peanut butter filling, and chocolate ganache on top. Such an easy summer dessert for cookouts, BBQs, and parties!" alt="Close up of sliced peanut butter cheesecake with chocolate topping on a serving platter" class="skip-lazy a3-notlazy no-lazyload dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner" data-no-lazy="1"></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="180" height="180" src="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-2-180x180.jpg" data-pin-media="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-2.jpg" data-pin-title="The Easiest Cheesecake I've Ever Made (No Bake!)" data-pin-description="No oven, no eggs, no stress. Just an ultra-smooth and creamy peanut butter cheesecake that sets up perfectly in the fridge. Add that chocolate ganache on top and it turns into the kind of easy summer dessert everyone goes back for seconds of! Perfect for summer BBQs, cookouts, Father's Day, and birthday dessert when you don't want regular birthday cake." alt="chocolate ganache being poured over no bake peanut butter cheesecake" class="skip-lazy a3-notlazy no-lazyload dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner" data-no-lazy="1"></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="180" height="180" src="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-3-180x180.jpg" data-pin-media="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-3.jpg" data-pin-title="EASY No-Bake Peanut Butter Cheesecake" data-pin-description="I’m not exaggerating, this no bake cheesecake tastes like a giant Reese’s! It’s ultra creamy, packed with peanut butter flavor, and topped with a rich chocolate ganache. If you love a good peanut butter chocolate dessert, this easy summer dessert is a must. The perfect no bake recipe for kids!" alt="Slice of no bake peanut butter cheesecake with chocolate topping on a serving platter, ready to be served" class="skip-lazy a3-notlazy no-lazyload dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner" data-no-lazy="1"></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="180" height="180" src="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-4-180x180.jpg" data-pin-media="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-4.jpg" data-pin-title="My Go-To Summer Dessert (No-Bake!)" data-pin-description="This easy peanut butter chocolate cheesecake will be the talk of any party! It’s smooth, rich, and full of peanut butter flavor without being heavy. No baking, no water bath, nothing complicated. Just a really good peanut butter dessert that always gets people asking for the recipe! Can be made ahead and frozen. You'll be asked to make this for every Mother's Day, Father's Day, cookout, BBQ, and birthday party!" alt="Close up of chocolate ganache drizzling over peanut butter cheesecake, with a second image of a single slice that's set and ready to serve" class="skip-lazy a3-notlazy no-lazyload dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner" data-no-lazy="1"></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="180" height="180" src="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-5-180x180.jpg" data-pin-media="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake-pin-5.jpg" data-pin-title="No-Bake PB Chocolate Cheesecake (So Easy!)" data-pin-description="I’ve brought this no bake cheesecake to a few summer cookouts now and it’s always the first dessert gone! It’s creamy, peanut buttery, topped with chocolate, and slices up beautifully. Such an easy summer dessert that looks impressive but is so easy to make! The perfect easy peanut butter dessert for BBQs, birthdays, or any time you’re feeding a crowd." alt="Serving platter with no bake peanut butter cheesecake and chocolate topping, one slice ready to enjoy" class="skip-lazy a3-notlazy no-lazyload dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner" data-no-lazy="1"></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="180" height="180" src="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/no-bake-pb-chocolate-cheesecake-pinterest-image-180x180.jpg" data-pin-media="https://handletheheat.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/no-bake-pb-chocolate-cheesecake-pinterest-image.jpg" data-pin-title="My Favorite No-Bake Cheesecake Recipe" data-pin-description="Like a giant peanut butter cup in cheesecake form! This peanut butter chocolate no bake cheesecake has a buttery graham cracker crust, ultra creamy peanut butter filling, and a layer of chocolate ganache topping. Perfect for summer when you don't want to turn your oven on! Simple and delicious, you’ll be asked to make this for every summer BBQ, cookout, picnic, and party!" alt="overhead view of cheesecake cut into slices with a cake server about to remove one" class="skip-lazy a3-notlazy no-lazyload dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner  dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-single" data-no-lazy="1"></div><div class="kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id30489_9c9cb5-c0 alignnone recipe-rundown wp-block-kadence-rowlayout"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-mobile-layout-row kt-row-valign-top">

<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column30489_8348b1-8a kb-section-dir-vertical"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<h2 class="kt-adv-heading30489_ee3123-c8 has-highlight-underline has-highlight-overlap wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading30489_ee3123-c8" id="toc-tessas-recipe-rundown"><span class="hth-highlight-inner hth-highlight-overlap"><em>Tessa’s</em> Recipe Rundown</span></h2>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-30489_ef57f7-ae"><div class="kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center"></div></div>



<p class="has--font-size" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0"><strong>Taste:</strong> Like a giant Reese’s peanut butter cup!</p>



<p class="has--font-size" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0"><strong>Texture:</strong> Super rich, smooth, and creamy.</p>



<p class="has--font-size" style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0"><strong>Ease:</strong> Very easy – no baking, no water baths, nothing difficult.</p>



<p class="has--font-size" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0"><strong>Why you’ll love this recipe:</strong> Simple and delicious recipe perfect for entertaining. </p>
</div></div>

