30.7295 8.10344 30.5826 8.16439 30.4293 8.16449H6.57031C6.41702 8.16439 6.27003 8.10344 6.16163 7.99505C6.05323 7.88665 5.99232 7.73966 5.99222 7.58637ZM27.2395 29.6827C27.2097 29.8096 27.1379 29.9226 27.0357 30.0034C26.9335 30.0842 26.8069 30.128 26.6766 30.1276H10.0052C9.87489 30.128 9.74831 30.0842 9.64608 30.0034C9.54386 29.9226 9.47203 29.8096 9.44231 29.6827L7.5092 21.5252H29.172L27.2395 29.6827ZM31.0074 19.6575V19.7908C31.0073 19.9441 30.9463 20.0911 30.8379 20.1995C30.7295 20.3079 30.5826 20.3688 30.4293 20.3689H6.57031C6.41702 20.3688 6.27003 20.3079 6.16163 20.1995C6.05323 20.0911 5.99229 19.9441 5.99219 19.7908V19.6575C5.99229 19.5042 6.05323 19.3573 6.16163 19.2489C6.27003 19.1405 6.41702 19.0795 6.57031 19.0794H30.4293C30.5826 19.0795 30.7295 19.1405 30.8379 19.2489C30.9463 19.3573 31.0073 19.5042 31.0074 19.6575ZM10.0052 17.9232C9.87489 17.9236 9.74831 17.8798 9.64609 17.799C9.54386 17.7182 9.47203 17.6051 9.44231 17.4783L7.5092 9.32074H29.172L27.2394 17.4783C27.2097 17.6052 27.1379 17.7182 27.0356 17.799C26.9334 17.8798 26.8068 17.9236 26.6765 17.9232H10.0052Z"></path></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">Storage &amp; Make ahead</span></h2>


<p><strong>Fridge: </strong>Store covered for up to 1 week.</p>



<p><strong>Freezer:</strong> Wrap the whole cheesecake or individual slices in plastic wrap, place in airtight container, and freeze for up to 1 month. Thaw in the fridge overnight before serving.</p>
